walk past the living room and go to the bedroom.

Pick up the knife on the counter.
Go across to the room, turn to the nightstand beside the wood shelf.
Slice the potato on the nightstand.
Place the knife on the sidetable to the left of the potato.

Go across at the door to the sink past the microwave.
Place the potato slice in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Go back to the room across from the microwave, turn to the sidetable.
Place the potato on the sidetable by the knife.

Put the knife on the sidetable.
Take the potato from the side table.

Put the piece of potato into the sink and washed it.
Then take it out and go to the bedroom.
